                <note rend="inline" type="source">818.00/846: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Honduras</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Jones</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-08-27T16:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 27, 1919, 4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your August 19, 6 P.M.</p>
                <p>Department cannot recognize Government of Quiros in Costa Rica, it being a
                    creature of Tinoco. Government must be formed in accord with old constitution
                    and free election must occur.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
